      • updateProbeConnections

        public static void updateProbeConnections(Design d,
                                          Map<String,String> probeToTargetNets)
        Updates a design containing an ILA (integrated logic analyzer) probe connections that already exist in a design.
        Parameters:
        d - The existing placed and routed design with an ILA.
        probeToTargetNets - A map from probe names to desired net names (full hierarchical names).
        pblock - An optional pblock (area constraint) to contain routing within a certain area.
